This paper is primarily focused on robot control using deep reinforcement learning, which falls under the category of robotics (cs.RO). The paper also discusses the use of deep neural network architectures, which is a common topic in machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of sensors and their fusion, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and control systems (cs.SY).
